dc_description_s: This data represents Buildings for Rock County, Wisconsin in 2022. [Polygons of building footprints in the unincorporated municipalities of Rock County, Wisconsin. Some building footprints in incorporated muncipalities where the building intersected the FEMA floodplains in 2008. Unicorporated areas are updated after orthoimagery and LiDAR flights.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison.
